I would restate it more like this:

Elves have (Belief/Sorceries/and Disciplines). The discipline of assertion
or creation is a very low level use of will with almost no flavor
of law or chaos. It is low level enough that it could be used to imitate a
Sla'ad or Kwuato cast (why would you want to do that ?). It would not be
