the Pattern consists of finding and accepting the correct packets and
    accepting the portion of the coordinates you need to use (very tricky).

    What is it like to walk the Pattern
    Very much like the chronicles  of Amber. The more skilled the walker the
more abrupt the jumps in reality can be. In effect the elf is reaching with
innate perceptions to determine what packets (and thus locales) are
available. The nearer realities (planes) have more packets in any given
area.

