"Bardic Tales Revision 6.0 ","This is a good start!  Write in with reactions and new proposals.

I am sending this to the people who are most likely to care about
changes to Rev 6.0 of Bardic Tales.  

I want to use this list as a forum for discussing those changes.  Your
input is needed- or who knows what I will do with the system!;-)

If you want off- please let me know!

Legitimate topics are proposed changes to the system, reactions to
proposed changes to the system, and really good dirt and gossip.. oh,
never mind.

			TOPICS:

NEW LEVEL FACTOR STAT BASIS

Right now the stat basis for level factor is (STAT-10) claculated as a
skill of that rank.  Now the stat basis for level factor will be:
	(STAT - 10)*2.
It makes stats more important in the beginning and beefs up lower level
characters a little.

NEW LEVEL FACTORS or LOSING SKILL FACTOR

I don't think so.  The level factors are a game mechanism to allow for
skill bleed and cross-skill support.  The way ""it really works"" would be
a logistical nightmare to model (because skills are grouped both by
neuro-muscular patterns of a very complicated  sort but also cognitive
associations and patterns which depend alot on the context the skills
are learned in, etc.  GROSS!)  Skill Factor is the level factor for
crafts and trades to go into- primarily those that are hands-on, skilled
labor.  It is also something of a hold-all for those skills you just
can't put anywhere else.!:-)  Am willing to hear suggestions that
enhance playability and are intuitively easy for the player to deal
with.

GUNS:

All guns are taking a -40 in rev 6.0.  They are also getting +4 damage.
You may also add your rank -2 as damage to your gun skill.

PRIMARY STATS:

I want to add build as a primary stat.  It already influences: defense,
weight, HTK, PAB, and MVM.  Why not make it a primary?

SO: 5 physical stats, and four mental.  And three attributes: height,
race, and gender.

I have decided to have age not be a stat with dependant variables in the
system.  Age is a special effect!;-) like hair color! 





