Starting at 8: 10=4,20=3,30=2,40=1
instead of: 10=4, 20=2, 30=1
Starting at 7 would yield: 8=4, 18=3, 28=2, 38=1

Speed does some to be an area of mystery for most people.  I have always found it rather straightforward but I am not sure if the straightforward system that I have been using is the actual BT system or if I just like math.


