"Re: More Gun & General BT Thoughts","I eagerly await rev 6.0.  Here are some final (?) thoughts...

Range Mods & Barrel Length:
   I promised to shut up and I am a man of my word.  *sigh*

HTK:
   I like the fact that body size has more to do with HTK in the new
