that STM is probably still overpowered in the STM/3 LVF/10 formula, but
I really believe that general life experience helps people understand,
evaluate and react to situations more quickly.  Obviously skill should
have more to do with it, which is why LFV AND Skill AND Secondaries go
into the total formula.  I think my original proposal was STM/2 +
