set-up!  I realize it would take a -20 to have 0 mods for a called shot
head but that is okay with me.   Now as to how called hot skills would
collapse into each other:  

Add the initial skill value of the skill ranks. Those are thus:

1-4 = 1-4
5   = 6
6   = 8
7   = 12
8   = 20 
9   = 36
10  = 68

You have an 8 and a 4?  Therefor ethat is 4 + 20 = 24.  You can
therefore convert that into a hmmm...
8=20, 9=36, the difference is 16, therfore every 1.6 ISL = a .1...if we
round up that gives you an 8.3 in called shot!;-)  Did anyone not 
