and not others?  OK, Skills that are high endurance burners are 
logical targets.  One of the effects of improved RNK in a skill like 
running is a smoother more fluid style that wastes less energy.  This 
benefit seems to me to start from the lowest levels, the increased 
efficiency of a RNK 4 runner vs. an unskilled runner is huge.  But 
the current system gives the RNK 4 person only a 11% better chance to 
roll a critical than the unskilled runner with the same stats runner 
( I assumed AGFs of 12 and 8 ).  The additional END gained by the RNK 
