Bardic Tales Revision 6.12 Change Sheet
January 12th, 1998

TABLE OF CONTENTS:
 CRITICALS/SUCCESS LEVELS [some NEW]
 ENDURANCE
 TIME                           [NEW]
 SPEED
 SETUP
 SUPPORT SKILLS
   INSTANT ATTACK
