No- the opposite.  Since you can buy ACT at 10% per ACT high level
characters would do that instead- because remember SL 1 is half the
high-level character's to-hit chance which is a lot of 10%s!!!!!    Only
someone who had less than a 60% chance would trade off  SLs- and then they
would run into the fact that their chance to succeed was so low as to make
it useless.  It was a good idea but falls apart in implementation.

