	relevant.  I do not really know them but If I had to guess this
	is what I would use:

	Activate Wizardry	8 cts
	Activate Kata		8 cts
	Activate Trance		1 minute

	Ki Focus		8 cts?		
		(I forget since Sigmund has a different version of Ki Focus
		than everyone else.  Is it 16? I think 8 is good)
	Florentine		4cts?
		(I think this should be very short since otherwise doing two
		actions together will take longer than doing them in serial)

	I think in general MODE skills should take longer to activate than
	a MODIFER skill in the same area.

	Just an interesting side diversion.  Stealth.

	Is stealth really a mode skill which you enter and then perform
	movement or some other action?  Is the skill SCF:Stealth (casting
