  k.. Create Warders - It strikes me that earth and order are linked.  This ability would take a set of earth spirits and dedicate them to enforcing the reality in an area.  It might be a specific reality or they may just be insuring that the conversation changes slowly.  This might be a real bummer for any chaos magic in the area or even any magic at all.
I am not sure how all of these would relate to the earth sorceries?  I figure S:Commune w/ Earth and S:Earth Form would still be good though they would cover the basic voice and form whereas their earthsinger counterparts would be much more persuasive/mobile.  I figure S:Summon Earth is way different than summon elemental but really important for those low earth environments (got to get the earthspirits there first befoer you can talk to them).  Grow would be enhanced versions of this.  I would think EarthShape and EarthBind would be considered crass by Earthsingers (why push when you can ask) but might still be good backup skills or perhaps the fast way of doing it and its OK if you apologize afterwards.

I do not see EarthSinging as fast and more involved with creating things (specialized earth spirits) than performing effects.

I suppose in the long term there might be interesting things to explore in terms of Dirt (Earth+Nature) and Magma (Earth+Fire) but for now this is my focus.
 
