    Based on conversations that Jim and I had on the way home last night
we think that we should do the following:

    1. Attempt to use Drawing to hide our ""packet"" emissions.
    2. Walk out in a tight group directly past an ""toads"" and change our
direction if it looks like we will cross paths with one.
    3. Move as far away from ANY entity that we possibly can.
    4. Although we think that Dau Pen would treat us better than Dof
Sifrin or Corellan, it is probably best to avoid any entities since
their outlook now is radically different from what it will be in the
future.  The only possible exceptions to this are likely to be whatever
corresponds to the Kerestaen or the Fates in this reality.
    5. When we get to an isolated spot experiment as much as possible
(without contacting other entities).  Determine when we are, what the
structure of reality is, magical rules, discipline rules.
    6. See if we can come up with a plan to get back
    7. If not, find a place to dig in and prepare to hold our own till
